#: ../../finding-jobs.rst:48
msgid ""
"`Job search spreadsheet <https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d"
"/1smDc1j5_1DZePYdC08cXBOZUNEvff5G8YECh-k_MiEI/edit?usp=sharing>`_"
