#: ../../finding-jobs.rst:57
msgid "Companies' own jobs pages"
msgstr ""

#: ../../finding-jobs.rst:59
msgid ""
"It's worth it to go straight to the source. Every company that's hiring "
"will have a jobs page. It's useful to see a job in the context of others "
"at the same company."
msgstr ""

#: ../../finding-jobs.rst:61
msgid ""
"Even if you discover a company's job advertisement via another site, have"
" a look at it on their site too. You might discover another role even "
"better suited to you, or run into some other advantageous information "
"related to the job. It's also where the information will be most up-to-"
"date."
msgstr ""

